mil.emp3.api.enums

Enum Property

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Property>
      • mil.emp3.api.enums.Property
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Property>

    public enum Property
extends java.lang.Enum<Property>
    This class enumerates all the configuration property keys used by properties parameter of different API calls. Each enumerated value requires a specific value type.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ENGINE_CLASSNAME

        public static final Property ENGINE_CLASSNAME
        This enumerated value defines the map's fully qualified class name for a new map. The key value pair requires a string value.

      • ENGINE_APKNAME

        public static final Property ENGINE_APKNAME
        This enumerated value defines the map's fully qualified android APK name where the class indicated in ENGINE_CLASSNAME is implemented. The key value pair requires a string value.

      • DEFAULT_SELECT_STROKE_COLOR

        public static final Property DEFAULT_SELECT_STROKE_COLOR
        This enumerated value defines the stoke color used to select features. The key value pair requires an IGeoColor value. The default color is yellow.

      • DEFAULT_SELECT_ICON_SCALE

        public static final Property DEFAULT_SELECT_ICON_SCALE
        This enumerated value defines the scale factor to use when an icon type feature is selected. The key value pair requires a double value. The default value is 1.2.

      • DEBUG

        public static final Property DEBUG
        This enumerated value defines the debug setting. The key value pair requires a boolean value and the default is false. Setting this value to true will generate additional log statements.

      • PROXY_URL

        public static final Property PROXY_URL
        This enumerated value defines the proxy url to be used when a feature or map service indicates useProxy set to true. The default value is null. The key value pair requires a string value.

      • MIRROR_CACHE_MODE

        public static final Property MIRROR_CACHE_MODE
        This enumerated value defines if the mirror cache is to be used and in what mode. The default value is MirrorCacheModeEnum.DISABLED. This property requires a MirrorCacheModeEnum value.
